lead_paragraph: While the expectations of his fans soared sky-high after Jordan Spieth's sensational 2015 campaign, the American feels much greater pressure from himself as he prepares for his Masters title defence this week.

headline.print_headline: Masters Champion Spieth Feels Pressure Only From Himself
headline.main: Masters Champion Spieth Feels Pressure Only From Himself
